summary: A self made Nord Preset: Elena Lothbrok
descriptionHtml:
[i][size=4]Hi Guys, it's my first upload and I thought I'd make a Preset of my own self made Character.[/size]
[size=4]Be sure to let me know if it doesn't work or if you get a different Face.
Also please post a Comment and let me know if it works.[/size][/i]

[size=3][i]Armor I used in Screenshots:[/i] [/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/42169/?][size=3]Demon Hunter Armor by Jojjo[/size][/url][size=3] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38053/?]Northgirl Armor
[/url]

[size=4][i][b]Requirement[/b]:[/i][/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Race Menu 3.0
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?]SkyUI[/url]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKES
[/url]
[size=4][i]Recommended Mods:[/i][/size]
SG Hair Pack 268 by HelloSanta (Google it) [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]
SG Female Textures Renewal[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrow
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2812/?]Better Females by Bella
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]Enhanced Character Edit[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSkyHair[/url]
[size=2][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?]ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer[/url][/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30/?][size=3]No More Blocky Faces[/size]
[/url]
[i][size=3]Installation:

[/size][/i]1. Download and unpack File (Elena Lothbrok Preset.jslot)
2. Copy "Elena Lothbrok Preset.jslot" into /Skyrim/Data/SKES/Plugins/CharGen/Presets
3. Load any working save file
4. Open the console and type "showracemenu"
5. Select Nord Race
6. Open slide option "presets"
7. Select the slot "Elena Lothbrok Preset"
8. Customize your character as you please and play

[b]If you don't have the "Presets" folder, just create one.[/b][s]

[/s]
[i]Future Mod:[/i]
I am working on making a standalone Follower of Elena[/size][/size][size=2].
Since it would be my first Mod ever it'll take some time.[/size]
